flowchart LR
  %% HackTrap AI Threat Monitor - Component Diagram

  subgraph Client["Frontend (Vite App)"]
    UI["index.html + styles.css<br/>Scrollable dashboard layout"]
    State["main.js<br/>State + render pipeline"]
    Map["Leaflet map<br/>Global marker visualization"]
    SocketClient["Socket.IO client<br/>new_event stream"]
    RestClient["Fetch client<br/>Polling + snapshots"]
  end

  subgraph API["Backend (Node.js + Express + Socket.IO)"]
    Server["server.js<br/>HTTP + WebSocket orchestration"]
    Generator["generator.js<br/>Session-based synthetic event generation"]
    Analyzer["analyzer.js<br/>Threat + intent + stage + prediction"]
    Profiles["profiles.js<br/>IP attacker profile store"]
    Memory["In-memory buffers<br/>Events + profile state"]
  end

  UI --> State
  State --> Map
  State --> SocketClient
  State --> RestClient

  SocketClient <-->|WebSocket: new_event| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/events| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/system-status| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/attackers| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/attackers/:ip| Server

  Server --> Generator
  Generator --> Analyzer
  Analyzer --> Profiles

  Generator --> Memory
  Analyzer --> Memory
  Profiles --> Memory
  Server --> Memory
